elow. An additional block by infiltrating behind the 3rd molar anaesthetises the long buccal nerve</li><li>Upper teeth often anaesthetised by injecting locally either side of the base tooth.</li></ul><br /><I>image illustrating position of inferior alveolar nerve block</I><br /><CENTER><table><tr><td align = 'left' colspan='2'><a data-fancybox class='fancybox' rel='group' href='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/fti013b.png'><img class='ajaximage' src='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/fti013.png'/></a></td></tr><tr><td valign='top' align='left'></td><td align='right'></td></tr></table></CENTER></div>\n\n\n<BR><BR><table style='width:100%'><tr><td>Australian dental journal</td><td style = \"float: right;width:115px;\"><button type=\"button\" style=\"\" id=\"link_like_51\" data-linkid=\"51\" data-rating=\"1\" class=\"rate-link btn btn-link\"><svg class=\"bi bi-hand-thumbs-up\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-hand-thumbs-up\"/></svg></button><span id=\"link_good_count_51\" class = \"link_good_count\" style=\"color:green; font-size:85%;\">0</span><button type=\"button\" style=\"\" id=\"link_dislike_51\" data-linkid=\"51\" data-rating=\"0\" class=\"rate-link btn btn-link\"><svg class=\"bi bi-hand-thumbs-down\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-hand-thumbs-down\"/></svg></button><span id=\"link_bad_count_51\" class = \"link_bad_count\" style=\"color:red; font-size:85%;\">0</span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/full/10.1111/j.1834-7819.2011.01312.x\">Applied anatomy of the pterygomandibular space</a></td></tr></table><br><br><table style='width:100%'><tr><td>Wikipedia</td><td style = \"float: right;width:115px;\"><button type=\"button\" style=\"\" id=\"link_like_50\" data-linkid=\"50\" data-rating=\"1\" class=\"rate-link btn btn-link\"><svg class=\"bi bi-hand-thumbs-up\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-hand-thumb